It has a long history

00:29:23.150 --> 00:29:25.600
and is our country's
first modern observatory.

00:29:25.600 --> 00:29:27.150
Located on the peak of Purple Mountain,

00:29:27.150 --> 00:29:29.470
it embodies
a strong traditional Chinese aesthetic.

00:29:29.470 --> 00:29:30.470
Next, we'll

00:29:30.800 --> 00:29:31.910
visit the summit.

